%% MuGate — Sequence: Schedule generation
%% Source: GeneratorController · GeneratorService · CombinationEngine · ScoringEngine
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant GeneratorController
    participant GeneratorService
    participant History as HistoryService / Curriculum
    participant Courses as CoursesService / CourseSections
    participant Scoring as ScoringEngine

    Client->>GeneratorController: POST /api/generate { semesterId?, preferences }
    Note over GeneratorController: authMiddleware
    GeneratorController->>GeneratorService: generateSchedules(userId, …)
    GeneratorService->>History: load AcademicHistory + CS_CURRICULUM
    History-->>GeneratorService: getEligibleCourses()
    GeneratorService->>Courses: load sections (sync/cache if needed)
    Courses-->>GeneratorService: CourseSection[]
    GeneratorService->>GeneratorService: build conflict-free combinations
    GeneratorService->>Scoring: score(SchedulePreferences)
    Scoring-->>GeneratorService: ScoredSchedule[] ranked
    GeneratorService-->>GeneratorController: ranked options
    GeneratorController-->>Client: 200 schedules
    opt user saves a choice
        Client->>Client: POST /api/schedules/save
    end
